1
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,560
These three bodies,

2
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:56,720
judging from the lividity and degree of decomposition,

3
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,979
have been buried for less than two weeks.

4
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,960
These bodies

5
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:04,720
were dug up in the back mountain by Constable Su and me.

6
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,919
Behind them hides an unknown secret.

7
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,240
Because of this,

8
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:14,680
four murders were triggered in one day.

9
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,360
I think it is very necessary for me to tell you

10
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:20,480
the real reason behind these murders.

11
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,560
Sixteen years ago,

12
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:28,850
Deputy Governor Cao was killed by his younger brother Cao Fang.

13
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:32,880
The newlywed Mrs. Cao gave birth to a son the following year,

14
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,240
named Cao Wen.

15
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:38,120
Mrs. Cao used all the property she received

16
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,840
to buy this house

17
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:43,520
and pinned all her hopes on her young son,

18
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:48,160
hoping that at sixteen he could emulate the talent of Cao Zijian,

19
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,560
composing a poem within seven steps,

20
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,220
becoming famous far and wide,

21
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,920
or have the intelligence of Cao Chong.

22
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,240
Weighing an elephant in childhood,

23
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,700
he showed his brilliance,

24
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,720
and became famous overnight.

25
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,840
He was expected to restore the family's honor

26
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,440
and live up to expectations.

27
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,360
Under such pressure,

28
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,840
Cao Wen did not write a good article.

29
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:10,040
But Lady Cao had already announced

30
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,920
that her son had written an essay

31
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,480
and it would be published soon.

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,640
So Lady Cao ordered her steward...

33
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,400
Recruited four poor scholars.

34
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:25,160
But these scholars from humble backgrounds left their hometowns

35
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,160
and came here

36
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:28,680
just to advance their studies

37
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:31,480
and earn some money to support their families.

38
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,160
The steward used the promise of high pay

39
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:36,220
to trick these scholars into ghostwriting for Cao Wen.

40
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,600
Scholars are honest by nature.

41
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,980
They never expected that coming here

42
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,920
would leave them with no way out.

43
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,380
Their way home was cut off.

44
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:48,000
One of the scholars wanted to go home.

45
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:51,760
The steward found out, killed him, and buried him in the back mountain.

46
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:54,840
Another scholar happened to see this,

47
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:58,140
so he wrote this book, 'The Scheme of the False Pregnancy'.

48
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:01,720
The manuscript was later handed over to Master Yuan.

49
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,680
To avoid further trouble,

50
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,720
at Master Yuan's suggestion,

51
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:09,560
Madam Cao killed all the scholars.

52
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:14,520
Writing a book is like a pregnant woman giving birth.

53
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,079
I said long ago

54
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,720
that he couldn't write such an article.

55
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,800
To complete a book,

56
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:34,080
they didn't hesitate to murder others

57
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:36,120
and steal their benefits.

58
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,520
Absolutely shameless.

59
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:51,720
Scholar Jiang, who is close to Madam Cao,

60
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:56,560
and Compiler Dong, who is in charge of revising this book.

61
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:59,090
Do you know about the bloody case behind this?

62
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,080
Actually,

63
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:09,000
I didn't have much interaction with Madam Cao.

64
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:13,600
She asked me to put in a good word for Cao Wen's work.

65
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,000
But as for other things,

66
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,480
I know absolutely nothing about them.

67
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:19,740
What about you?

68
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:22,360
I... I'm just a compiler.

69
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,920
The texts Madam Cao handed over

70
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:28,160
were all discussed and copied by Workshop Master Yuan.

71
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:31,320
I was only responsible for having the workers bind them.

72
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,600
As for what's behind this,

73
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,120
how would I know?

74
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,600
Such evil deeds

75
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,880
are truly intolerable by heaven.

76
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,440
Envoy Jueming,

77
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,360
since things have come to this,

78
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:47,880
I just want to know the outcome.

79
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,840
Cao Wen,

80
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,880
answer me honestly now.

81
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:01,200
How many scholars did you hire to write your books

82
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,960
in your residence?

83
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,840
Four.

84
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:09,340
But there are only three bodies here.

85
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:14,160
I believe there is another body

86
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,440
which the suspect has dug up.

87
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,770
Just like what is written in this book.

88
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:24,360
The murderer in the book takes Consort Zhao's child away.

89
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:28,320
I believe the real suspect

90
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,760
will also dig up his closest relative's bones.

91
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,159
Don't move!

92
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,920
Behave yourself!

93
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,159
Let me go!

94
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,840
I will tell you the truth.

95
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,600
Fine.

96
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,520
Killing them

97
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,360
and leaving you as a puppet

98
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,720
to let the world see

99
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:14,000
the hypocritical and vicious true face of the Cao family

100
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:17,240
is just as satisfying.

101
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,800
Are you confessing?

102
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,640
I didn't plan to live.

103
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,480
These beasts

104
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,000
deserve to die.

105
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,040
Who... who on earth are you?

106
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:44,159
I am Zhang Chiwen's biological brother.

107
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,560
My real name

108
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:50,000
is Zhang Renjiu.

109
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,320
Before my brother left,

110
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,720
he said he would concentrate on writing here.

111
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,760
Unexpectedly, once he entered this villa,

112
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,840
there was no news from him at all.

113
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:13,040
I was heartbroken at home.

114
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,640
After inquiring around,

115
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,920
I found out that

116
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:23,680
the other scholars who came to the villa with my brother,

117
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:27,520
their families had also come to this villa looking for them.

118
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,040
But this villa's manager

119
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,799
was very unreasonable.

120
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,039
He forcibly drove them away

121
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,840
and kept insisting that

122
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,840
these scholars had never been here.

123
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:47,680
At that time,

124
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,800
I learned that

125
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:56,720
Cao Wen published a new book,

126
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,320
'The Fake Pregnancy Plot'.

127
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,640
I went to great lengths

128
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:07,440
to finally purchase this book.

129
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:10,040
When I read it carefully,

130
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,080
I felt the writing style

131
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:14,320
was very similar to my brother's.

132
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,360
I couldn't help but wonder

133
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:19,200
if this book was written by him.

134
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:23,320
To find out the truth,

135
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,440
I sneaked into the villa

136
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,920
and got a job as a servant.

137
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,920
After entering the villa,

138
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,800
I searched everywhere

139
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:35,920
and finally dug up several corpses in the back mountain.

140
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:52,080
You lied to me again.

141
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,160
Didn't you say

142
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,560
you'd be back soon?

143
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:09,000
Brother.

144
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,880
I was heartbroken

145
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,800
and quietly moved

146
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:28,080
my brother's remains into my room to hide them.

147
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,960
Then I thought carefully.

148
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:36,040
Many things are related to this 'Fake Pregnancy Scheme'.

149
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,280
Isn't what's written in that book

150
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:41,960
an allusion to this tragedy?

151
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:48,440
Consort Zhao, who miscarried in the book,

152
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:51,320
corresponds to Cao Wen.

153
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:55,560
The Consort's mother corresponds to Madam Cao.

154
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:56,760
And

155
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,720
Imperial Physician Sun, who informed the Emperor,

156
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:03,520
doesn't he correspond to Workshop Master Yuan, who pushed the book?

157
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,850
And Xiao Shunzi, who was busy running around,

158
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:10,520
doesn't he correspond to the villa's manager?

159
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,320
In that case,

160
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:15,480
I secretly forged a dagger exactly like the Six-Star one

161
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:18,480
to confuse the order of my killings.

162
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,450
How did you know about me and Madam?

163
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,760
The book says it all.

164
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:25,720
Imperial Physician Sun had an affair with Consort Xian's mother.

165
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:28,200
What do you mean?

166
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,600
Did you really see the killer?

167
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,280
Who is it?

168
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,920
It's me.

169
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,920
If things go smoothly this time,

170
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,360
after I kill the last person,

171
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:25,880
I will definitely reveal the truth to everyone.

172
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:29,120
Even if I fail,

173
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,720
I will make it known to everyone,

174
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:37,400
so the truth won't be buried underground forever.

175
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,280
In that case,

176
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:42,360
why did you kill Gu Yitong?

177
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:48,770
He is a distant relative of the Cao family.

178
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:52,080
Look at how he flatters them.

179
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:57,120
It doesn't hurt to kill one more.

180
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,360
I was also forced by my mother.

181
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:11,000
I can't write anything.

182
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:13,520
I can't write anything at all.

183
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:18,000
She insisted on making me the pride of the Cao family.

184
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:21,080
What could I do?

185
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,800
You say your brother is pitiful.

186
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,800
Am I not pitiful?

187
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:31,800
I am nothing but a walking corpse.

188
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,960
Since I was young,

189
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:38,600
no one has ever truly cared about me.

190
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,440
They only cared if I had fame,

191
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,240
and if I could bring glory to the Cao family.

192
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:47,120
No one ever considered my feelings.

193
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,840
But I know I am good for nothing.

194
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:54,720
She insisted on me having this fame.

195
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,520
At this point,

196
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:06,000
I can't pretend anymore.

197
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:22,760
Jueming.

198
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:23,960
The boat has reached the ferry.

199
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,920
Let's go.

200
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:28,840
Sit down. Have another drink with me.

201
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,480
Let's go. We're in a hurry.

202
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:33,200
This fine wine of Yayuanju is a rare treat.

203
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,280
If you don't drink it now,

204
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:36,140
you'll rarely get a chance again.

205
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,880
We can come again.

206
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,160
What?

207
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,600
Here.

208
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,160
This is really good.

209
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:53,640
Sister.

210
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:01,400
This was found in Liu Renjiu's room.

211
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:04,160
I believe that in this world,

212
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:06,600
no one wants to kill voluntarily

213
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,520
unless they have no other choice.

214
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,880
Just like me.

215
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,720
Aren't my hands

216
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,360
covered in blood now?

217
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:21,000
I believe he had no other choice either.

218
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:23,200
Just like last night,

219
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:26,040
I am willing to bear all this for him.

220
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,840
According to the order in the book,

221
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:32,560
the last person Liu Renjiu intended to kill was not Gu Yitong,

222
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,920
but Cao Wen.

223
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,640
He would kill Cao Wen using the same method,

224
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,960
and then place this fourth volume.

225
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,160
Su Lang.

226
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,040
You committed a copycat murder.

227
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,760
After disposing of the body, you came to us.

228
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:52,680
You didn't expect that we had already caught the suspect.

229
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:54,000
What reason would I have to kill someone?

230
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,440
It really wasn't me.

231
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:57,240
Jueming, Miss,

232
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:58,960
we found another body.

233
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:06,080
So you panicked.

234
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,240
Yes.

235
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,080
According to your plan,

236
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:13,840
you could frame Liu Renjiu for Gu Yitong's death

237
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:15,320
without any problems.

238
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:17,200
But where it went wrong is,

239
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,480
the timeline doesn't match.

240
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,880
He lives in the west wing,

241
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,080
and I live in the utility room.

242
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,640
Besides, how could I kill him in such a short time

243
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:28,560
and then return to the pond by the utility room to throw away the dagger?

244
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:30,760
If you hadn't finished dealing with it.

245
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,440
You should have a book

246
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:35,800
missing the fourth volume on you.

247
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:02,380
I wanted to take it with me when I left.

248
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,640
Why did you do this?

249
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,960
He is not human.

250
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:42,280
I remember you are here to search for the suspect's tools.

251
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:45,680
This has nothing to do with you, right?

252
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:48,160
Who drew this?

253
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,640
I drew it.

254
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:53,200
Why? Do you like it too?

255
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,860
I am Honglian's adoptive father.

256
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,760
Honglian is a child I took in.

257
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:02,880
I raised her all these years.

258
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:07,080
How could I let a poor constable like you have her so easily?

259
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:10,460
How much money do you want to let Honglian go?

260
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,040
Ten guan?

261
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:13,060
A hundred guan?

262
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:14,640
A thousand guan?

263
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:19,320
I will give her to anyone I need to curry favor with.

264
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:22,600
So you came to the villa this time

265
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:25,640
just to push Honglian to Cao Wen.

266
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,720
Exactly.

267
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:29,440
One night is all it takes.

268
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:33,120
I'll give you money.

269
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:34,360
I can marry Honglian.

270
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,440
Silly boy.

271
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:41,320
Who would sell the goose that lays golden eggs?

272
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:44,720
Honglian is my golden goose.

273
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:49,480
If you want to sleep with her, it's simple.

274
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,320
Just pay.

275
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,400
Since you all know,

276
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:07,640
why didn't you expose me last night?

277
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:13,280
This character 'xue' must be written straight and true.

278
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:15,200
There must be rules.

279
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:18,240
Come, take a look.

280
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:19,880
Look at what I wrote.

281
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:21,320
Do you see?

282
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:23,040
Wow, so beautiful.

283
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:25,120
Alright, let me see what you wrote.

284
00:19:27,360 --> 00:19:28,640
Not bad.

285
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:32,400
This stroke, it can't stick out here.

286
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:34,720
Writing is like being a person.

287
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:37,240
You must be proper.

288
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:40,280
Be straight and true.

289
00:19:40,360 --> 00:19:43,320
Be reasonable and organized.

290
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:49,040
My eldest son is back from the villa.

291
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,280
How was it?

292
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,160
Did you benefit a lot this time?

293
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:55,480
Wow.

294
00:19:55,520 --> 00:19:57,280
You brought so much good food.

295
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:00,960
Freshly bought sesame cakes. Try them.

296
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:04,280
Pickles.

297
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:07,360
Sesame cakes with pickles.

298
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,280
It's my favorite.

299
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,600
All right,

300
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:12,330
put down your brushes, you two.

301
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:14,960
Let me see how you did.

302
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,080
Let's see yours.

303
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,440
You did quite well.

304
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:23,360
You followed my instructions. It's standard,

305
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:25,040
straight,

306
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:27,280
and aligned.

307
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:28,000
Not bad.

308
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:29,280
You can eat now.

309
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,760
Let's see yours.

310
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:36,840
It's a bit messy.

311
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,880
Not very standard.

312
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:39,960
Correct it next time.

313
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:40,960
Got it.

314
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,800
Let's eat first.

315
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:43,920
Here.

316
00:20:46,840 --> 00:20:49,300
Why aren't Jueming and the eldest lady here?

317
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:52,090
There was a murder in the villa.

318
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:54,720
They went to the government office to deal with it.

319
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,280
Another murder?

320
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,440
Who died?

321
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,880
Madam Cao.

322
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:04,840
And

323
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:06,760
their butler.

324
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:09,410
And Master Yuan of the Moxiang Bookstore.

325
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:15,360
It's so hard for people to stay alive nowadays.

326
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:18,280
Why do they have to commit murder?

327
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:22,400
What's wrong?

328
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:23,700
Why aren't you eating?

329
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:25,800
I wrote several characters wrong today.

330
00:21:25,800 --> 00:21:27,320
I want to punish myself.

331
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,840
In a person's life,

332
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:34,680
they always make some mistakes, big or small.

333
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:37,240
As long as you can correct them, it's fine.

334
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:38,240
Okay?

335
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:38,920
Come on.

336
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:39,840
Go and correct them.

337
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:40,640
Eat today.

338
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:41,960
No need to punish yourself.

339
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:42,840
Mm.

340
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,280
Chief Constable Su.

341
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:47,360
You'll be busy from now on.

342
00:21:58,280 --> 00:22:00,010
Go buy some clothes for Mother.

343
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:02,000
I see her clothes are worn out.

344
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,120
And you too.

345
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,560
You always wear this one.

346
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:06,880
Alright.

347
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:08,560
We have food and clothes.

348
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:10,440
We don't need your money.

349
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,520
You need money now.

350
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:14,000
Keep it for yourself.

351
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:15,960
Is it good?

352
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:17,480
Yeah, it's good.

353
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:30,280
There's still so much left.

354
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,280
Why did you stop eating?

355
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,640
I'll go to the government office.

356
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,960
Brat.

357
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:43,240
Since you all know,

358
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:46,560
why didn't you expose me last night?

359
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:51,160
We wanted to give you a chance.

360
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,620
I'll go surrender myself.

361
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:07,520
But I want to see my father one more time.

362
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:10,760
You can write more words when you're full, right?

363
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:11,800
Yes. Yeah.

364
00:23:30,040 --> 00:23:31,320
I was wrong.

365
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:11,400
It's okay.

366
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,000
Wait for me.

367
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,560
I will figure something out.

368
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,240
Su Lang.

369
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:44,800
Just go.

370
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:47,640
We are over.

371
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:02,480
Your portrait has been seen by so many people,

372
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,600
and your father...

373
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:08,960
Do you despise me?

374
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:13,680
We can't go back.

375
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,560
Just leave.

376
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:19,480
You said you would protect me.

377
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:23,640
Was everything you said a lie?

378
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,520
Just treat it as a lie.

379
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:31,680
Go.

380
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:38,680
Leave!

381
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,440
Someone told me

382
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:05,480
that a person's palm prints represent their destiny.

383
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:07,050
Do you believe in fate then?

384
00:26:07,560 --> 00:26:09,440
I'll believe it if my fate is perfect.

385
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:10,480
If it's bad,

386
00:26:10,520 --> 00:26:11,850
why should I believe it?

387
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:16,760
But the family I was born into decided my fate.

388
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:19,560
Just like a shadow.

389
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:23,040
I can't shake it off.

390
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:40,840
Then I'll hide with you.

391
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,280
Hide from the sunlight,

392
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:45,080
and let's hide our shadows together.

393
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,280
I am a murderer now.

394
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:57,240
There's no going back.

395
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:06,160
Do you remember that day

396
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:10,080
we were on the swings together?

397
00:27:14,760 --> 00:27:16,880
I said I would always protect you.

398
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:23,280
This time, I broke my promise.

399
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:29,960
Honglian,

400
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:34,280
I want to introduce you to my dad and my friends.

401
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:37,560
Tell them we are together.

402
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,000
Honglian.

403
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:52,080
I hope you can always be this happy.

404
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:54,840
I will always protect you too.

405
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,760
Maybe in the next life.

406
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:07,040
I will protect you in the next life.

407
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,960
As for my father,

408
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,760
my mother told me everything after I grew up.

409
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,560
She told me

410
00:28:21,360 --> 00:28:24,360
that my father was killed by her own brother, Cao Fang.

411
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,720
After Cao Fang died,

412
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:30,280
the constable in charge of the case came to see her.

413
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:36,840
He really used a Gu insect.

414
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:38,080
That's right.

415
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:40,360
This is what we found in Cao Fang's room,

416
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:42,480
the vessel containing the dead Gu insect.

417
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:44,640
I married here from Yunnan.

418
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:47,560
This kind of Gu insect only grows in Yunnan,

419
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:50,000
and if it leaves its natural habitat,

420
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:52,080
it won't live for long.

421
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:54,600
But Cao Fang had never been to Nanzhao,

422
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,920
nor did he have any friends from Nanzhao.

423
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,720
So, Madam, you mean...

424
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:05,160
someone else was directing Cao Fang.

425
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:14,480
Madam,

426
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:19,280
did Vice Governor Cao go anywhere recently?

427
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,960
Did he make any friends?

428
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:28,360
One day, he went out on foot alone for a long time.

429
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:31,080
When he came back, his shoes were covered in mud.

430
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:33,940
When I asked, I found out he went mountain climbing.

431
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:35,400
I reckon

432
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,680
the only mountain nearby that can be a day trip

433
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:40,800
is Niutou Mountain.

434
00:29:41,120 --> 00:29:42,480
When did this happen?

435
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:47,880
About three months ago.

436
00:29:48,120 --> 00:29:50,880
He usually takes a sedan chair for long trips.

437
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,440
He wouldn't go alone,

438
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:54,360
so it made a deep impression on me.

439
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:55,920
I found it very strange,

440
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,840
but I didn't dare to ask.

441
00:29:59,080 --> 00:30:00,440
Why would a person

442
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,200
go to Niutou Mountain alone?

443
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,160
My mother said.

444
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,970
After my father's funeral,

445
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:11,880
we moved out of Shaoyin Mansion.

446
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:15,320
Since then, that constable never came again.

447
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:21,820
Why are you asking me this all of a sudden?

448
00:30:24,320 --> 00:30:27,000
The constable who questioned your mother has gone missing.

449
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,840
I want to know where he went.

450
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:31,920
Lord Li,

451
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:34,480
I truly have no way out.

452
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,920
That is why I boldly came to beg you for help.

453
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:42,560
I beg Your Excellency to save my son's life.

454
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:48,320
I have worked diligently for the Yamen for half my life,

455
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:51,720
never daring to slack off,

456
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:54,760
and solved countless cases.

457
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:56,360
But I never expected that today,

458
00:30:56,360 --> 00:31:00,520
a case would fall upon me.

459
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:04,040
My son had a moment of folly

460
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:05,200
and was blinded,

461
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:08,640
committing the grave crime of murder.

462
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:12,920
But this child grew up by my side.

463
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:17,200
He only wanted to follow in my footsteps

464
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:22,480
and contribute to the Yamen and the court.

465
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:24,600
He is not bad by nature,

466
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:27,520
nor is he a heinous villain.

467
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:30,360
I beg Your Excellency to show mercy.

468
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:31,560
Mr. Su,

469
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,080
please get up.

470
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:34,640
Get up.

471
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:39,760
Mr. Su, take your time to speak.

472
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,480
Lord Li.

473
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:45,600
I am not an ignorant person.

474
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:50,040
I also know how strict the law is.

475
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:55,120
But I only hope you, Lord Li,

476
00:31:56,160 --> 00:32:00,080
can spare Su Lang's life.

477
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:04,240
Just let him live.

478
00:32:17,760 --> 00:32:20,680
This is the petition we wrote for Su Lang.

479
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:23,800
He has helped us solve many major cases.

480
00:32:24,280 --> 00:32:25,940
The difficulty of those cases

481
00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:28,160
is still vivid in our minds.

482
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:31,040
We only hope you can present this document

483
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:32,600
to the new magistrate,

484
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:34,280
so he may consider his past merits

485
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,760
and show leniency.

486
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,880
Mr. Su.

487
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:41,680
Su Lang has committed a felony of murder.

488
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:44,120
According to the laws of the Tang Dynasty,

489
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:46,050
this crime is punishable by death.

490
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:49,760
I also know you are extremely anxious right now.

491
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:53,880
As for whether his past contributions to the yamen

492
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:55,650
can lead to a reduced sentence,

493
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:56,840
this matter

494
00:32:57,200 --> 00:33:00,360
depends on the new magistrate's consideration.

495
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:03,010
Although I am the Deputy Mayor of Henan

496
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:05,290
and in charge of local affairs,

497
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:09,640
if I rashly influence the direction of the case,

498
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:11,560
it would be inappropriate

499
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:13,320
and contrary to the law.

500
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:18,160
All right, I can only truthfully convey the facts of this case

501
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:21,520
and Su Lang's past merits

502
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:24,080
to Magistrate Zhao.

503
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,480
The subsequent ruling

504
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:29,880
will be entirely up to him to decide according to the law.

505
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,880
What the final result will be

506
00:33:32,040 --> 00:33:33,520
is hard to predict.

507
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:37,220
You still need to mentally prepare yourself

508
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:39,080
and await the verdict.

509
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:45,050
Master, Lu Yun, Vice Director of the Ministry of Rites, asks to see you.

510
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:51,720
Vice Director Lu was also invited to the villa yesterday.

511
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,920
He is familiar with the details of the case.

512
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:55,450
Invite him in immediately.

513
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,210
Deputy Governor Li.

514
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:06,920
I am Lu Yun, Vice Director of the Ministry of Rites.

515
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:08,480
I take the liberty to come here today

516
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,280
to discuss an important matter.

517
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:12,840
Vice Director Lu, please have a seat.

518
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,719
Please.

519
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:20,360
Vice Director Lu, you've gone to such great lengths.

520
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,880
What is this about?

521
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:25,400
Yesterday, I gathered with you all at the villa,

522
00:34:25,679 --> 00:34:27,280
and we experienced a murder case together.

523
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:30,159
Your crime-solving methods are truly amazing.

524
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,880
Now Su Lang has violated the law

525
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:33,000
and is imprisoned.

526
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:35,639
And you are looking for a way out.

527
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:37,639
I happen to have a cold case here

528
00:34:37,639 --> 00:34:38,969
that remains unsolved.

529
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:42,000
If you can solve this case...

530
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:44,920
It can certainly win a sentence reduction for Su Lang.

531
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,679
I will truthfully report to the Ministry of Justice,

532
00:34:46,679 --> 00:34:49,800
so they can reduce Su Lang's sentence at their discretion.

533
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:52,040
Or I can report to Dali Temple,

534
00:34:52,239 --> 00:34:55,040
and wait for their fair and strict investigation.

535
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:57,720
What case are you referring to, Vice Director Lu?

536
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:59,520
You might as well speak plainly.

537
00:35:01,160 --> 00:35:02,490
The national treasure,

538
00:35:03,080 --> 00:35:05,280
the theft case of the Glazed Pearl.

539
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,760
Mr. Lu.

540
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:11,640
I'll send someone to get Jueming right away

541
00:35:11,640 --> 00:35:13,400
to listen to your analysis of the case.

542
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:14,960
We'll take this case.

